column2: "Ah, and it seems you've brought more losers with you. Gahahaha!"
"Gettemhart, just what are you up to?"
"Isn't it obvious? I'm having myself a wonderful little picnic."
"Stop screwing with us! Did you cause that rumbling?"
"Can it, twerp. Sheena! Is it ready yet?"
"That's... the Clarissa! It was supposed to have been lost. What's it doing here?"
"It's already been put into motion? But if the seal has been broken, then everything..."
"If the seal is broken, then everything is lost. We need to get her away from the Clarissa!"
"You get it, right? The party's just about to get started."
"<%me>! It excites you, too, does it not? The malevolent vibe that permeates this place?"
"Gone insane? I was never particularly sane in the first place!"
